oil prices continued to fall on Friday , after concerns about a high supply overshadowed a report indicating that China &apos;s energy @-@ intensive manufacturing sector is growing .
in December , Europe &apos;s electronic trading unit in the New York Mercantile Exchange fell by 14 cents to $ 96.24 per barrel .
