he said NotW uses three methods to investigate stories investigative : telephone hacking , surveillance , and confrontation .
the publisher is personally involved in the third method .
obviously he knows of the second , the monitoring , otherwise it cannot be .
what about the first ?
do he know about the phone hacking ?
he disputes that , but we say : &quot; and if he knew it . &quot;
