meanwhile , former Chefreporter Neville Thurlbeck and former reporter James Weatherup oversaw the surveillance of Pawlby &apos;s movements .
on 18 June 2005 Coulson left her with a voicemail with the following content : &quot; I have a story that we want to bring out tomorrow , about which I would like to talk to Charles . &quot;
