but , according to statistics , I am a black sheep in Halloween .
the majority of Americans - 158 million to be precise - celebrate Halloween this year , spending a total of $ 6.9 billion on sweets , costumes , and decorations , according to the US Association of Retailers ( NRF ) .
one thing I look forward to every Halloween is the trend .
the costumes will amount to about 1.2 billion of the $ 6.9 billion spent , according to the NRF .
this year , exciting , inanimate objects are the last cry .
women no longer have to dress in sexy clothes , they can now also embody seductive food such as pizza , hamburgers or carrots .
