the only thing we do not want to consume is the sweet Candy Corn , yet 15 million kilograms are sold for Halloween , according to the National Association of confectionery producers .
that is about nine billion corn grains .
it is a mystery that I have not yet been able to resolve .
nothing belongs to Halloween more than houses where it spurs .
they have great names such as &quot; Terror Disabled the Walls &quot; ( which , incidentally , is in a real prison ) , &quot; Howl @-@ O @-@ Scream &quot; and &quot; The House of Shock . &quot;
